data.description: CHEAPER THAN RENT! Perfect for investors, those downsizing, or first-time home buyers. Located near parks, schools, shopping, SCAFB, and downtown STL this updated charmer has everything you need to make yourself at home. Fresh paint and newer flooring guide you through the cozy living room, full bath, and 2 nice sized bedrooms.The eat in kitchen offers excellent counter and cabinet space with a semi-open concept. Through the attached 1 car garage, steps lead you to the full unfinished basement that provides additional storage or potential for additional living space. Exiting to the backyard you will find a covered patio, shed for even more storage, and a huge fenced backyard.  Additional features include a new water heater & HVAC! Buyer to verify all MLS data. Buyer's agent should independently verify all MLS data, which is derived from various sources and not warranted as accurate.
